As of 2.9, Lucene offers specialized {{NumericField}} and {{NumericRangeQuery}} to perform indexing and quering of numeric values. JIRA {{NumberRangeSearcher}} should start using them for better performance of such queries. As {{NumericField}} is not a {{Field}} instance (rather, it is implementation of Lucene's {{Fieldable}}) this may also help expose places in JIRA indexing/searching code where {{Field}} is incorrectly used instead of {{Fieldable}}.

